snippet.textDisplay:
You guys brought me such Christmas joy with this end 2019 video. I did have to internally laugh thinking back to like the first videos Steven and Andrew were in together. Steven like a puppy 🐶 running around excited nearly looking like he might lick an annoyed Andrew's face. Andrew wasn't comfortable with food touching that you'd both eating, he was annoyed with the concept of "toasting" food/folks etc. and now you guys really do have a shared friendship and an enjoyment beyond an "I know him from the office". I think this growth shows and makes each episode so enjoyable and almost like "your sad it's over" because it's fun to share the laughs and smiles. I think Adam rounds it out but I do enjoy when you actually get a little estrogen on the show with any of the girls that kinda help out with different things between sound and interpreting for you guys. I love your travels to places I'll probably never see. I do kinda think you guys could have a full episode on my home town. Come to Portland and enjoy the Pod/Food cart scene. 😊
Merry Christmas and Happy New Year to you all! Cheers!

I think this growth shows and makes each episode so enjoyable and almost like "your sad it's over" because it's fun to share the laughs and smiles. Merry Christmas and Happy New Year to you all! Cheers!
